HEADWORD: panting
<hw>panting</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Breathing laboriously or
convulsively.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> gasping, out-of-breath(predicate), pursy,
short-winded, winded.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

